@startuml
title analysis.normalize - Semantic normalization
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

component "normalize.py\npython -m analysis.normalize" as norm
database "results/\nraw JSONL" as results
database "results_normalized/\nnormalized JSONL" as out
file "manifest-<run_id>.json (optional)" as mf

results --> norm : raw rows per tool
mf ..> norm : expected tools/metrics\n+ profile hints
norm --> out : normalized rows:
note right of out
Normalization goals:
- unify field names (metric/tool/variant/component)
- canonical component types
- clean numeric values/status
- attach run_id + parameters
end note

@enduml
